        <p>ActiveCampaign vs Brevo: scenario 3 — gift message field abandoned mid-flow. At $73 AOV and 55% margin, full-price recovery contributes $40.15 vs $32.52 after a 19% code (Δ $7.63). Ladder touch 3 favors SMS urgency; watch for discount on email one before trust proof. Email 1 ~93m, email 2 ~47h, SMS branch ~5h for opted-in only.</p>
